commit.message:
iwmmxt.md (movv8qi_internal, [...]): Add mem = reg alternative.

	* config/arm/iwmmxt.md (movv8qi_internal, movv4hi_internal,
	movv2si_internal): Add mem = reg alternative.

From-SVN: r138146
